I commend the work of Robert Mueller and his investigation, and I look forward to a complete and speedy end so Americans know the facts regarding Russian attempts to undermine trust in our democratic institutions.
It is time those involved pay the price. I welcome these indictments and the demonstration of the due process provided by our judicial system that is systematically denied to Russian citizens.

Our law enforcement and intelligence services confirm that Russian individuals and entities have engaged in a long-running effort to interfere in our electoral process in a malicious attempt to undermine our democracy and discredit the United States on the world stage.

Our American style of democracy is the envy of the world and must be protected from foreign attack in all its forms. Consumed with their own power, the Russia kleptocracy has made it clear they hate the free and fair choice of the people to choose their leaders.
